# ============================================
# EkagraFocus Environment Configuration
# ============================================
# 
# This file is optional. EkagraFocus works
# completely offline without any configuration.
#
# To enable advanced AI features with a local LLM,
# configure one of the options below:

# ============================================
# Option 1: Embedded LLM (Recommended)
# ============================================
# Set this to the path of a GGUF model file
# for local AI inference without Ollama
#
# Download GGUF models from:
# https://huggingface.co/models?search=gguf
#
# Popular models: Mistral-7B, Neural-Chat-7B, etc.
#
# Example:
# LLM_MODEL_PATH=/path/to/model.gguf
# LLM_MODEL_PATH=C:\Users\YourName\models\mistral-7b.gguf

LLM_MODEL_PATH=

# ============================================
# Option 2: Ollama (Alternative)
# ============================================
# Set this to use Ollama for local LLM inference
# Make sure Ollama is running before starting the app
#
# Install from: https://ollama.ai/
# Start with: ollama serve
#
# Recommended lightweight model: phi
# Optional timeout for the Ollama request in milliseconds
#
# Example:
# OLLAMA_HOST=http://localhost:11434
# OLLAMA_MODEL=phi
# OLLAMA_TIMEOUT_MS=30000

OLLAMA_HOST=
OLLAMA_MODEL=phi
OLLAMA_TIMEOUT_MS=30000

# ============================================
# Notes:
# ============================================
# 1. Both LLM options are optional
# 2. App works with pattern matching if neither is set
# 3. Embedded LLM is faster than Ollama (if available)
# 4. Model file should be GGUF format (.gguf extension)
# 5. For setup help, see SETUP.md
